msgstr "Un map-mask de exemplo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:513
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The blue component (in RGB model) of a country's color identifies the "
#| "country: index 0 is country 0 in the onu.xml file, index 1 is country 1, "
#| "&etc;. White (0xFFFFFF in RGB) identifies the absence of country (sees "
#| "or, why not, no man's lands)."
msgid ""
"The blue component (in RGB model) of a country's color identifies the "
"country: index 0 is country 0 in the <filename>onu.xml</filename> file, "
"index 1 is country 1, &etc; White (0xFFFFFF in RGB) identifies the absence "
"of country (sees or, why not, no man's lands)."
msgstr ""
"O compoñente azul (no modelo RGB) da cor dun país identifica o país: o "
"índice 0 é o país 0 do ficheiro onu.xml, o índice 1 é o país 1, &etc;. O "
"branco (0xFFFFFF in RGB) identifica a ausencia de país (mares ou, por que "
"non? terra de ninguén)."

